competent, where he discovers who he is and what his team is, where
he learns how to win because he has learned why he lost. It's where
Bill Parcells will lead the Jets against the Jacksonville Jaguars
next Sunday in an American Football Conference divisional playoff,
the beginning of what could be his fourth journey to the Super
Bowl. By Dave Anderson.
