<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-03 16:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6108 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-INDIA-AIDS-ART-3TAKES     01-03 1049
