argue its national championship credentials. But if Florida State
wins, there could be a number of once beaten teams on Jan. 5 who
could claim a piece of the national championship. When all is said
and done, the mythical national championship is just that. But with
the Bowl Championship Series set for at least three more years,
there won't be a chance anytime soon. (Barnhart, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) 25.
