   INDIA-AIDS (Calcutta, India) _ The government plans to use a
project that has distributed condoms among sex workers in Calcutta
as a model for all of India, hoping to keep the rate of HIV
infection relatively low in a country of almost a billion people.
2700 words. By Celia S. Dugger.
