-- Israeli police officers carrying boxes from a home on
Jerusalem's outskirts where members of a American-based apocalyptic
cult and their children were living. Israeli police officials
Sunday arrested eight members of the Concerned Christians cult, who
officials say were planning to mark the millennium by committing
suicide or provoking their own killings in the streets of
Jerusalem. (Rina Castelnuovo/New York Times Photo)
