<P>
   BRITAIN-EURO (London) _ Holding back on the brink as it has at
every turn towards European integration, Britain observed the birth
of the euro single currency as a nation apart this weekend, its
leaders mute even as the banks that power the City of London
financial district prepared to trade the new money by the
trillions. By Alan Cowell.
